data.description: This home is a 5 bedroom, 2 bath, and 2 car garage bi-level with lots of space and nice sized rooms.  Large lot, fenced backyard with a 390 Sq. ft. work shed and walk-up basement.  Washer and Dryer included.  Spacious garage.  Hardwood floors in the bedrooms and appear to be beneath the carpet in the upper living room.  Alley access to the backyard with a gate to accommodate RV or additional parking  With a little love this would be a great home, all it needs is some TLC.
